-But it's different with him.

251
00:16:24,765 --> 00:16:26,331
His case was an accident.

252
00:16:26,365 --> 00:16:27,798
-What has become of that boy?

253
00:16:27,831 --> 00:16:30,598
Tell me, what are
you doing right now?

254
00:16:30,631 --> 00:16:32,231
Aren't you trying
