256
00:16:34,131 --> 00:16:37,631
Re-extermination is
what you people do.

257
00:16:37,665 --> 00:16:38,698
Rage and anger.

258
00:16:38,731 --> 00:16:41,498
Rage is all I have left.

259
00:16:41,531 --> 00:16:42,998
-Hey, is everyone all right?

260
00:16:43,031 --> 00:16:43,465
-Huh?

261
00:16:43,498 --> 00:16:44,498
A new enemy?

262
00:16:52,465 --> 00:16:54,398
-Don't let go of my hand.

263
00:16:54,431 --> 00:16:55,531
-I won't.

264
00:16:55,565 --> 00:16:57,731
Haven't you heard what
I've been telling you?

265
00:16:57,765 --> 00:17:01,865
Didn't I say it enough?

266
00:17:01,898 --> 00:17:05,531
-You and I are one.

267
00:17:05,565 --> 00:17:06,831
-You!

268
00:17:06,865 --> 00:17:09,931
-Near-death happiness.

269
00:17:09,965 --> 00:17:11,931
-Move, you're in the way.

270
00:17:11,965 --> 00:17:13,898
-Motor gears.

271
00:17:13,931 --> 00:17:16,365
-Pierce through our Buso Renkin.

272
00:17:28,298 --> 00:17:30,565
-Looks like his energy--

273
00:17:30,598 --> 00:17:31,898
-Is being released.

274
00:17:31,931 --> 00:17:33,365
-Ah!

275
00:17:33,398 --> 00:17:36,265
-Victor is being restored
back to a human being.

276
00:17:43,065 --> 00:17:43,998
-It failed!

277
00:17:44,031 --> 00:17:45,965
-Wait!

278
00:17:45,998 --> 00:17:48,431
His skin is returning to
it's original olive tone.

279
00:17:48,465 --> 00:17:50,798
The White Kakugane is
definitely working.

280
00:17:54,931 --> 00:17:58,365
-I'm afraid it's power is
not enough to offset my Black

281
00:17:58,398 --> 00:18:02,365
Kakugane now that I've
entered my third stage.

282
00:18:02,398 --> 00:18:04,565
Listen, boy, just
like me, you've

283
00:18:04,598 --> 00:18:06,831
been hunted down by
the Alchemist Army

284
00:18:06,865 --> 00:18:09,831
and almost killed by
those closest to you.

285
00:18:09,865 --> 00:18:13,165
But if still intend to fight
me in spite of all of that,

286
00:18:13,198 --> 00:18:15,065
then be my guest.

287
00:18:15,098 --> 00:18:16,831
-Kazuki, get ready.

288
00:18:16,865 --> 00:18:17,831
Don't let go.

289
00:18:17,865 --> 00:18:20,165
You and I are one.

290
00:18:20,198 --> 00:18:22,931
Remember, when you die,
I will die with you.

291
00:18:25,665 --> 00:18:28,065
-I'm sorry.

292
00:18:28,098 --> 00:18:30,265
I'm really sorry, Tokiko.

293
00:18:30,298 --> 00:18:31,965
I cannot keep that promise.

294
00:18:42,331 --> 00:18:46,092
I really am truly sorry.

295
00:18:49,720 --> 00:18:51,587
-Kazuki!

296
00:18:51,620 --> 00:18:53,053
NARRATOR: Muto, no!

297
00:18:53,087 --> 00:18:53,987
-Kazuki Muto!

298
00:19:00,420 --> 00:19:04,320
-Energy full blast!

299
00:19:04,353 --> 00:19:07,087
-My dear Victoria.

300
00:19:07,120 --> 00:19:09,153
-Yes, Mama?

301
00:19:09,187 --> 00:19:11,620
-If you should ever
meet your Papa,

302
00:19:11,653 --> 00:19:17,920
tell him-- tell him that I
loved him till the very end.

303
00:19:23,053 --> 00:19:27,220
-Hm, but Mama, if you happen to
be the one to meet Papa first,

304
00:19:27,253 --> 00:19:30,187
please tell him this for me.

305
00:19:30,220 --> 00:19:35,153
That I can live on and survive
even if I am all alone.

306
00:19:54,220 --> 00:19:55,720
BRAVO (VOICEOVER): Kazuki.

307
00:19:55,753 --> 00:19:56,553
-Kazuki.

308
00:19:56,587 --> 00:19:57,953
-Kazuki.

309
00:19:57,987 --> 00:19:59,887
-That man.

310
00:19:59,920 --> 00:20:00,753
-That boy.

311
00:20:00,787 --> 00:20:02,087
-Thank guy.

312
00:20:02,120 --> 00:20:04,887
-Kazuki Muto.

313
00:20:04,920 --> 00:20:06,253
-Mr. Muto.

314
00:20:06,287 --> 00:20:08,553
-The Warrior Muto.

315
00:20:08,587 --> 00:20:09,953
-Kazuki Muto.

316
00:20:09,987 --> 00:20:11,253
-Kazuki.

317
00:20:11,287 --> 00:20:12,687
-Kazuki.

318
00:20:12,720 --> 00:20:14,520
-Kazuki.

319
00:20:14,553 --> 00:20:15,320
-Kazuki.

320
00:20:15,353 --> 00:20:16,787
-Kazuki.

321
00:20:16,820 --> 00:20:17,920
-Kazuki.

322
00:20:17,953 --> 00:20:18,420
-Kazuki.

323
00:20:25,887 --> 00:20:26,653
-Big brother.

324
00:20:38,520 --> 00:20:40,120
-I'm impressed.

325
00:20:40,153 --> 00:20:41,853
On the lifeless
surface of the moon,

326
00:20:41,887 --> 00:20:43,820
the energy drain is useless.

327
00:20:43,853 --> 00:20:46,653
That was a very good strategy.

328
00:20:46,687 --> 00:20:50,087
Now, it's a match of
pure strength and skills.

329
00:20:50,120 --> 00:20:52,987
However, whether
you win or lose,

330
00:20:53,020 --> 00:20:55,453
you will no longer be
able to return alive.

331
00:21:00,053 --> 00:21:04,820
This determination of yours,
where does it come from?

332
00:21:04,853 --> 00:21:05,620
-Where else?

333
00:21:08,387 --> 00:21:09,787
It comes from that planet.

334
00:21:12,553 --> 00:21:20,320
You see, back there, there are
many people I want to protect,

335
00:21:20,353 --> 00:21:23,820
including the most
important person in my life.

336
00:21:27,587 --> 00:21:31,820
Ever since-- ever
since that one day,

337
00:21:31,853 --> 00:21:35,453
up until this very moment, even
though so much has happened,

338
00:21:35,487 --> 00:21:39,420
all I can remember now
are the good times we had.

339
00:21:50,520 --> 00:21:54,353
TOKIKO (VOICEOVER):
Kazuki Kazuki.

340
00:21:59,720 --> 00:22:00,653
-You idiot!

341
00:22:00,687 --> 00:22:03,053
I'll never forgive you, Muto.

342
00:22:03,087 --> 00:22:06,453
How dare you make
Tokiko suffer like this.

343
00:22:06,487 --> 00:22:12,853
-So now, there is no one left
who knows who I really am,

344
00:22:12,887 --> 00:22:16,320
and who would call
me by my name.

345
00:22:16,353 --> 00:22:16,787
-Kazuki.

346
00:22:24,047 --> 00:22:27,547
[theme music]

347
00:23:54,257 --> 00:23:57,324
TOKIKO: What could be left
for me on this planet?

348
00:23:57,357 --> 00:24:00,657
On this planet, where
you are no longer exist?

349
00:24:00,690 --> 00:24:04,790
But this is the world
you risked your life for.

350
00:24:04,824 --> 00:24:08,324
Next time, no one could
ever take his place.

